[CLS] <s>Hello, I have been feeling very overwhelmed with school.</s><s>Hello. I totally understand being stressed out by school. I am currently in a Ph. D. program and it can be overwhelming. Do you have any hobbies to help with your stress?</s><s>I do like to read, but I haven' t had enough time. I have been going on walks more frequently.</s><s>It sounds like you do a lot of activities that are solitary. Have you considered maybe partaking in a similar activity, like a book club, where there is more interaction with people?</s><s>No, I did not consider that actually. I do enjoy my alone time since I am so busy and I have a toddler, but maybe doing something more sociable would be good.</s><s>Being busy, especially with having a small child can make you feel lonely, enhancing the stress you feel from school. Participating in social events geared toward your interest might be able to connect you to people with similar feelings!</s><s>I think so too. I never thought of it like that.</s><s>I' m sure that you are trying your best to be both a good student and a great parent. It is understandable that you may not have considered those options.</s><s>Yes I constantly think of my son and family, and I didn' t think involving myself in sociable activities would be beneficial. [CLS] <s>Just found out my position will be eliminated in January. Freaking out! 1.</s><s>Wow. So you' re being laid off soon?</s><s>Yes. Apparently the company just can' t continue to operate and pay all of us. So my position will be gone. They said they may be able to hire me back after all the Covid stuff, but couldn' t guarantee it 2.</s><s>I' ve been laid off many times. Never gets easier. Will they give you severance? Do you qualify for unemployment? Any offer for retraining or job assistance?</s><s>It is hard emotionally - as well as financially. I tried calling the unemployment office to find out what help they may have but no one answered me. 3.</s><s>Your not getting the unemployment office to respond seems to be a common problem. They weren' t geared up for this. Fortunately, the online portal has been helpful for many. What are your skills and strong points?</s><s>I will have to look at that. [CLS] <s>Hi there, how are you today?</s><s>I'm doing ok. Have been feeling a bit anxious about my job lately.</s><s>Is this because of the pandemic? I know a lot of people are worrying about their jobs because of this.</s><s>I think it's partially due to the pandemic. I am struggling progressing at my company and have been up for a raise for a year now that still hasn't gone through. It's making me feel like they don't value me.</s><s>I am sorry to hear that. So, I hear you saying that you feel you are not being valued for your work?</s><s>Yeah exactly. I want to feel like I am an important member of the team and right now I'm not feeling that and it makes me feel like I don't have a future with this career anymore. But now is not the time for a career change.</s><s>No I guess that it isn' t. Have you tried talking to your employer about this? I have tried connecting with other students but many are just as confused as me, especially when it comes to showing the work part. You mentioned online sites, how accurate and helpful are those?</s><s>Khan Academy is absolutely fantastic! Did they have any reviews on how helpful they are in the math field?</s><s>No but I am a former math teacher and I would give them to my students!</s><s>Okay, that is great. I dont know what to do.</s><s>I can understand your situation very well as it happened with me in past. In this scenario you should take small breaks to relax your body and mind. You will feel better.</s><s>I hope so, I am very scared to lose my job, as my boss says I am not capable to do my work if i get stressed out so easily.</s><s>Time is running bad for all of us. [CLS] <s>Hi.</s><s>Hello! How are you doing today?</s><s>I' m doing better now that I have someone to chat with! I' ve been feeling down and anxious about getting older lately because I' ve lost may parents and I' m worried about losing my aunts.</s><s>I understand, you feel like your losing everyone close to you and wondering about your own mortality now as well?</s><s>Exactly, I worry about losing my aunts because they are in their 70s and 80s. [CLS] <s>Hi. I am worried about my exams.</s><s>Exams are a stressful time. What seems to be the problem?</s><s>I do not feel like I am properly prepared, even though I have studied..</s><s>I can assure you that countless students including myself have gone through the trials of studying for exams and do feel overwhelmed but it passes. Have you studied?</s><s>I have studied. However, I still feel like I am not prepared. One big problem is that I have no quiet place to study..</s><s>I get it, distractions can be challenging to overcome at times. Have you thought about going to a library, or a book store?</s><s>I have not. Both of those are great suggestions. I wonder if I should take the time to walk to the library( 30 minutes), or just continue to study? Maybe, I know as much as I can know. The anxiety is too much.</s><s>If it helps you study then the library may be worth the time and effort. Sometimes we can stress out over worrying about not having enough time to study. But trust the work you have done and you will know if it is enough.</s><s>This is very good advice. Have you completed college?</s><s>Yes, and it wasn' t easy but with hard work, it is completely doable. And you have the power within yourself.</s><s>What do you think will happen if I fail this test?</s><s>Sometimes it is not about the amount of studying, but the way you study. I like reading my textbooks and highlighting the important parts and then rewriting them so they become ingrained in me. But let us not jump the gun, you haven' t failed anything.</s><s>Very true. Thanks for reminding me. I think I worry more about the outcome than I need too.</s><s>Don' t forget to breathe. Exams are stressful but I would suggest don' t cram everything to the last minute. Usually the hour before the exam, I do something else.</s><s>Very good advice. Any suggestions on what I can do?</s><s>Stay calm, believe in yourself, start your studying early so you are not cramming everything in the last few days.</s><s>Great Advice.. But, in the one hour prior to the exam, do you have any advice on something I can do to calm my nerves?</s><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad>[CLS]  about my exams.</s><s>Exams are a stressful time. [CLS] <s>hey.</s><s>Hello, my name is Amber, how are you doing?</s><s>I could be better.</s><s>What' s been happening?</s><s>I just had a baby 2 months ago and I have been struggling with my physical appearance and dealing with my mental health.</s><s>Is part of that the weight gain from pregnancy? I' m sorry to hear you are going through this, it sounds like a very tough time for you.</s><s>I didnt keep much weight from the pregnancy but its the loose skin that makes it very challenging to accept and to love my self.</s><s>Oh that is understandable. I am a mother, and remember worrying about the same thing.</s><s>My depression has gotten worse since having my son. I feel a constant feeling that i' m not a good mother. I feel worthless and having a constant feeling that I don' t deserve my son.</s><s>I can tell you from personal experience that loose skin, stretch marks, and loosening of" other parts" do all self correct with time. You will feel better about your body again when they do.</s><s>How did you cope with post partum?</s><s>I was fortunate not to experience depresion. But I totally went through self doubt, wondering if I was being a good enough mother, and feeling" not up to" the task.... it' s the hardest job in the world, being a mom, and so exhausting the first while. [CLS] <s>Good morning! What can I help you with today?</s><s>Hi, i' ve been feeling really depressed lately and I' d like to talk to someone about it.</s><s>That is very understandable. Depression is tough to deal with.. Do you have specific things that are causing you sadness right now or is it an overall feeling of being sad?</s><s>It' s a bit of everything. I' ve recently lost my job and I' m just really worried about how my bills are going to get paid. I feel so tired, you know?</s><s>I totally understand. Losing your job is a very rough thing to go through, I' m sorry that happened to you. Feeling constantly at red alert is taxing both mentally and physically.. There is a concept called Maslow' s hierarchy of needs, and sometimes I find it useful to think about if my needs are being met, and which is lacking. Which is to say, obviously financial security is your primary need at the moment, but there are other needs you must attend to as well, including your physical comforts.. In times of great stress and upheaval, there is only so much you can do. The rest is worry, a hamster running in a wheel, a huge output of energy that does nothing at all..</s><s>Yeah that makes sense but I' ve spent so much time thinking about my finances that I' ve sort of burned myself out. Like I have no energy even to be thankful for the other little stuff.</s><s>That makes sense. [CLS] <s>Hopefully I find an employer that sees a quality workforce over other things, its getting pretty discouraging. I seem to be getting blocked at application level for employment, it seems my skills are mostly being put out to contract work now, which is not something I am familiar with.</s><s>I see. Maybe there are some qualification programs in your local area, or maybe at the local university or college where you could take classes? There is a career development center at my local university that is open to everyone, maybe you could see if they would review your resume and give you some objective feedback? Students love a good live subject: -)</s><s>Wow I have never thought about that! That sounds awesome and like it would be great help, also trying something new would feel nice instead of filing the same stuff into applications!</s><s>You should explore what resources your city/ county/ province may offer for job seekers. It is in the best interest of almost every community that its members have have jobs and feel useful, so you may find some valuable information and maybe some connections.. Oh! And what I always tell everyone who is looking for a job: Apply UP! Don' t ever think is something above your level. Apply UP! They may admire your temerity and invite you for an interview just to see who you think you are: -)</s><s>My spirits are going up just having this conversation and looking forward to the community outreach. Hopefully it helps lift this gloom that has been over me for months. I loved my previous job but due to bad management it was taking a toll on everyone employed.</s><s>I am glad to hear you are feeling a little better! Yes, bad management is so toxic. Even with great coworkers in a job you love, horrible management can ruin it quickly.. You seem like you are open to trying new solutions and putting in the effort to up your competitive level. Stay positive and take care of yourself mentally and physically, and I think you will be successful..</s><s>I think that is truly when I started feeling down, productivity was high but it mattered not to those in charge it was never enough. [CLS] <s>how are you feeling today?</s><s>Not so great. I broke up with my boyfriend a couple days ago.</s><s>So you have been feeling down since the breakup a couple days ago?</s><s>Yes I have. I just do not know what to do with myself anymore.</s><s>I can relate to this heartache as I have gone through similar breakups in my life. The important thing is that we pick ourselves up after something like this.</s><s>I just do not know where or how to start the process.</s><s>It can be really hard sometimes! It appears that you possess the strength and motivation to be able to pick yourself back up. The factthat you are reaching out for help shows you have the motivation and desire to work to get better!</s><s>I do not want to feel like this forever!</s><s>Studies indicate that emotions felt immidiately after a breakup eventually subside with time. It is important to take care of yourself in the mean time. Do you have any hobbies?</s><s>Yes. I love to read.</s><s>So you like to read? Have you thought about reading self - help books on perhaps depression?</s><s>I do read self help books.</s><s>Have the books provided you any benefit?</s><s>Not really.</s><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad>[CLS] <s>how are you feeling today?</s><s>Not so great. I broke up with my boyfriend a couple days ago.</s><s>So you have been feeling down since the breakup a couple days ago?</s><s>Yes I have. I just do not know what to do with myself anymore.</s><s>I can relate to this heartache as I have gone through similar breakups in my life. [CLS] <s>Hi there, how are you doing today?</s><s>I am okay, I am very worried about my friend. I believe she is abusing prescription drugs.</s><s>Oh no, why do you think she is abusing them?</s><s>I don' t think it, I guess I actually know she is. She use to have a heroin problem and went on methadone. She has since started taking anxiety medicine in order to get high.</s><s>Thats a tough spot to be in, ive actually been both sides of that coin.</s><s>I think I know what I need to do, It is just hard.</s><s>It is hard. Unfortunately you can only try to direct them to stop for so long before it can really damage your own well being, which should come first.</s><s>I agree, and after going through this in the past with her, I just can' t sit and wait for the train crash. she feels like she is doing nothing wrong because she has valid prescriptions. I feel like I should just cut her off completely, I don' t have time for her drama. What do you suggest?</s><s>I would actually suggest just that. If you have tried, or do not even feel like going down that path. Then that is your decision. You should look out for yourself!</s><s>True, I definitely do not need to be caught up in her mess. I have too much to lose. I just feel bad like i am abandoning her.</s><s>The thing is with drugs, that person already abandoned themselves. Its kind of like a blackhole where everything gets sucked into their life.</s><s>True, I know she has to want to help herself. [CLS] <s>Hello.</s><s>Hi! How are you today?</s><s>I have been better.</s><s>It sounds like you might be upset. Can you tell me what's going on?</s><s>My ex partner and I broke up a long time ago because they cheated on me. Now they will not stop contacting my friends and family and posting about me on social media.</s><s>That sounds difficult and stressful. [CLS] <s>Hello there, would you be able to give me some advice? The first lockdown was bad enough but the second has really thrown me into despair. I simply cannot cope without being able to see friends and family for much longer..</s><s>I would be glad to. What is troubling you?</s><s>I have run out of coping mechanisms!</s><s>I completely understand and had similar experiences. What were some ways you tried to interact with people last shut down?</s><s>I use facebook quite a lot and it helps but it cannot compensate for face to face contact. I really need to be able to see people.</s><s>Digital contact does have its limitations. Could you meet with people outside at a distance?</s><s>Well, part of the problem with that is that I am not sure what the rules are any more! We have been told so many different things that I am out of the loop.</s><s>I understand. Try sticking to the basics to make it less stressful. Wear a mask outside at a distance.</s><s>I always do wear a mask.. I think we legally have to:). I really miss little things like going out for coffee or to the gym though. It makes me feel like will never be the same again.</s><s>Have to talked about this with friends? They may be feeling the same way. Just talking this out with the may be reassuring.</s><s>I have a little bit but I don' t want to burden them. The other aspect is that it is making me anxious about many others things too. [CLS] <s>hello.</s><s>Hi, I am hear to listen today. How are you?</s><s>i am not well.</s><s>I am sorry to hear that and I have felt that way myself. Has something unusual happened that you would like to share?</s><s>i have an exam coming up annd i dont wanna fail.</s><s>I understand and that can be very concerning. Have you been preparing for the test or have you had anyone to study with? Better than usual. What about you?</s><s>I am good thank you. Is there anything you want to talk to me about?</s><s>Yes. Recently, I broke up with my fiance. <s>Hello.</s><s>Hello. [CLS] <s>I think your suggestions are very helpful. A vacation is currently out of the picture due to COVID. I want to try having deep conversations, but I don' t know where to start.</s><s>Start by talking about whats going on. Tell her how you think you guys should spend more time with her. Or that you dont want to lose her. Ask her if there is anything she might want to discuss. She maybe having issues shes afraid to talk about.</s><s>I think you hit upon something. She is quite hesitant in talking about issues. Do you have any thoughts about marriage counselling? We' ve never tried that.</s><s>I think that would be a good idea. Having the chance to get things out and getting more advice is always helpful. Make sure you leave any issues at common ground.</s><s>If my wife is the one having issues with conversations, do you think a male or female therapist/ counsellor would be better? I want her to feel comfortable expressing herself.</s><s>Most likely a female therapist would be better. Nobody understands a woman more than a woman.</s><s>I think that sounds like a safer choice. I was also hoping if you have suggestions for me personally. I am quite depressed and I am having problems getting through the day.</s><s>I suggest taking one step at a time. I wouldn' t rush through things. I would suggest sitting down and talking through some things that are going on. Maybe taking some time away from work. Going out and spending time with each other as much as you can. If you guys think you may need a marriage counselor, I highly recommend it. [CLS] <s>Hello.</s><s>Hello.</s><s>How may i help you today?</s><s>I have a co worker who sleeps all the time at his desk. I physically work hard everyday.</s><s>I can understand how you are feeling.</s><s>It makes me mad. No one says a word to him, he just sleeps and gets paid for it.</s><s>Has anyone else noticed him sleeping all the time at his desk?</s><s>My boss said( I have been there for five years) to me one day did I see DE sleeping at his desk? I was floored that it seemed he never saw him do it before. How could he not?</s><s>That is really weird how can someone not see him sleeping at his desk.</s><s>Very weird. I am one of the oldest men there and I am always expected to jump in and do work that is manual labor. Very frustrating to see someone else just sleeping.</s><s>Have you talked to your co worker about it?</s><s>It really would not be my place, it would be up to my boss. He obviously said nothing..</s><s>if your boss said nothing to him then maybe you should step up and say something even though you are right that is not your place.</s><s>I keep hoping that one of the upper management team will walk by one day and see him.</s><s>Your boss does not sound like a good boss at all and not doing his job correctly.</s><s>Definitely not being fair across the board, in my eyes.</s><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad><pad>[CLS] <s>Hello.</s><s>Hello.</s><s>How may i help you today?</s><s>I have a co worker who sleeps all the time at his desk. [CLS] <s>Hello.</s><s>Hello! How' s it going? How can I help you today?</s><s>Hi. It has been better.</s><s>We all have those days:/ what' s bothering you?</s><s>I can' t seem to get motivated.</s><s>It sounds like your having trouble giving yourself that little push to get the wheels turning. I' ve totally been there. What do you feel is the reason?</s><s>I don' t feel like it is worth it.</s><s>I understand, I' ve been there before. You just have to take one step at a time and not overwhelm yourself. Have you tried any tools to help you get going?</s><s>What kind of tools would you suggest?</s><s>What I find that works is to make out a list of all the things you want to accomplish and the possible steps you need to get there. It also helps to let someone know how you feel like a friend or relative, you would be surprised that being open with people can open up new doors in life.</s><s>I can talk to my friends sometimes. I have big goals but can' t seem to get little things right.</s><s>You feel like your friends don' t listen or care? And trust me you are not alone. I am going through that as well. [CLS] <s>Hi. I am worried about my exams.</s><s>Exams are a stressful time. What seems to be the problem?</s><s>I do not feel like I am properly prepared, even though I have studied..</s><s>I can assure you that countless students including myself have gone through the trials of studying for exams and do feel overwhelmed but it passes. Have you studied?</s><s>I have studied. However, I still feel like I am not prepared. One big problem is that I have no quiet place to study..</s><s>I get it, distractions can be challenging to overcome at times. Have you thought about going to a library, or a book store?</s><s>I have not. Both of those are great suggestions. I wonder if I should take the time to walk to the library( 30 minutes), or just continue to study? Maybe, I know as much as I can know. The anxiety is too much.</s><s>If it helps you study then the library may be worth the time and effort. Sometimes we can stress out over worrying about not having enough time to study. But trust the work you have done and you will know if it is enough.</s><s>This is very good advice. Have you completed college?</s><s>Yes, and it wasn' t easy but with hard work, it is completely doable. [CLS] <s>Hello.</s><s>Hi.</s><s>May I know what is wrong?</s><s>I' m just feeling very overwhelmed with all the shutdowns. I' m a stay at home mom and have 4 kids. Managing day to day is hard..</s><s>It sounds like it must be stressful to be locked in all day with children.</s><s>Yes it is.
